(1, 'About Us', '&lt;div class=&quot;container&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-12&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Gotong Royong Fund is an Indonesian crowd funding platform that specializes in community fundraising, for both Indonesian individuals and organizations, seeking funding for social impact campaigns, educations, health, and the arts.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:rgb(0, 0, 0)&quot;&gt;Gotong Royong Fund is a sub-division of Yayasan Pendidikan Cerdas Madani Indonesia (YPCMI), which was established in 2010. YPCMI is social foundation providing training and education in investment and fund management. YPCMI&amp;rsquo;s mission is to enhance the awareness of investment education globally.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:22px&quot;&gt;Founder&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Marsekal Madya TNI ( Purn ) Prof. Dr. Ir Ginanjar Kartasasmita&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;Indonesian Politician who was a former of President&amp;rsquo;s Advisory Council (2010 to 2014), He was a Chairman of State&amp;rsquo;s Advisory Council (2004 to 2009), a former of Coordinating Minister of Economics, Finance, and Industry during the Development Reform Cabinet. Moreover, he was a former Ministry of Energy and Mineral Resources (1988 to 1993)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Adi Sasono&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;Former Cooperative Minister and Small Medium Enterprise during the Development Reform Cabinet, a General Secretary in 1990&amp;rsquo;s era, and a community leader of Civil Society Organizations&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Marzuki Usman&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;Economy Practical who was a former Ministry of Tourism, Arts, and Culture during the Development Reform Cabinet and a former Ministry of Investment / Chairman of the Investment Coordinating Body in 1999, duplicating as a former Ministry of Forestry and Plantation replacing Mr. Nur Mahmudi Ismail in 2001&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Soegiharto&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;Former Ministry of State Minister for State Enterprise during United Indonesia Cabinet (October 2004 &amp;ndash; Mei 2007). Commisioner of PT. AJB Bumiputra (2012 &amp;ndash; now)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Barcelius Ruru&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Bahrul Choiri&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Rifda Choiri&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Stanislaus Say&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Jamien A. Tahir&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Ferry Sudjono&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Tee Teguh Kinarto&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Mindo Sitorus&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Hismand Abubakar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Abraham Lembang&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Alexander Gee&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Hasan Zein Mahmud&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Erry Firmansyah&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Hernamawati&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '&lt;div class=&quot;container&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-12&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Gotong Royong Fund adalah sebuah wadah penggalangan dana (Crowd Funding) yang memberikan ruang bagi pemilik proyek dan donatur, baik individual maupun organisasi, di bidang sosial, pendidikan, ide kreatif, dan banyak lainnya untuk mencapai tujuan yang sama.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:rgb(0, 0, 0)&quot;&gt;Gotong Royong Fund adalah bagian dari Yayasan Pendidikan Cerdas Madani Indonesia (YPCMI), yang didirikan sejak tahun 2010. Yayasan ini merupakan lembaga sosial yang bergerak di bidang edukasi dalam hal pengelolaan dana, sesuai dengan misi YPCMI yaitu mengembangkan pendidikan di bidang investasi secara menyeluruh.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:22px&quot;&gt;Pendiri / Founder&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Marsekal Madya TNI ( Purn ) Prof. Dr. Ir Ginanjar Kartasasmita&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;Politikus Indonesia yang menjabat sebagai anggota Dewan Pertimbangan Presiden (2010 s/d 2014), mantan ketua Dewan Pertimbangan Daerah (2004 &amp;ndash; 2009), dan juga mantan menteri ekonomi, keuangan, dan indusrti pada era Kabinet Reformasi Pembangunan. Sebelumnya pernah menjabat sebagai Ketua Dewan Pertimbangan Daerah (2004 s/d 2009)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Adi Sasono&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;Mantan Menteri Koperasi dan UKM pada era Kabinet Reformasi Pembangunan, Sekretaris Umum pada tahun 1990-an ,dan juga tokoh LSM dalam berbagai aktivitas kemasyarakatan&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Marzuki Usman&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;Praktisi ekonomi yang piawai, merupakan Menteri Pariwisata, Seni dan Budaya (Menparsenibud) di era Presiden BJ Habibie di tahun 1998-1999 merangkap Menteri Peningkatan Investasi (Meninvest) dan Kepala BKPM tahun 1999, serta menjabat sebagai Menteri Kehutanan menggantikan Nur Mahmudi Ismail di tahun 2001&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Soegiharto&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;Mantan menteri negara BUMN di Kabinet Indonesia Bersatu (Oktober 2004 &amp;ndash; Mei 2007). Komisaris PT. AJB Bumiputra (2012 &amp;ndash; sekarang)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Barcelius Ruru&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;Presiden Komisaris PT Jababeka Tbk sejak tahun 2006. Ketua Prakarsa Jakarta hingga 2003 dan Sekretaris Menteri Negara BUMN hingga tahun 2004. Selain itu, ia adalah mantan Direktur Jenderal Badan Usaha Milik Negara (1995 &amp;ndash; 1998) dan mantan Ketua Badan Pengawas Pasar Modal (1993 &amp;ndash; 1995)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Bahrul Choiri&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Rifda Choiri&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Stanislaus Say&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Jamien A. Tahir&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Ferry Sudjono&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Tee Teguh Kinarto&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Mindo Sitorus&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Hismand Abubakar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Abraham Lembang&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Alexander Gee&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Hasan Zein Mahmud&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Erry Firmansyah&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;Hernamawati&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n'),
(2, 'FAQ', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#008000&quot;&gt;Question:&lt;/span&gt; What is a Crowdfunding?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Answer&lt;/strong&gt;: A crowdfunding is a collection of investors &amp;ldquo;crowd&amp;rdquo; to fund an initiative projects, can be a non-profit, a charitable or commercial or a start up company.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#008000&quot;&gt;Question:&lt;/span&gt; What is GotongRoyongFund&amp;rsquo;s platform?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Answer&lt;/strong&gt;: Our platform is a user-friendly and serves as a &amp;ldquo;network intermediaries&amp;rdquo; which brings together the project initiator and the crowd globally.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#008000&quot;&gt;Question:&lt;/span&gt; Why do people decide to use GotongRoyongFund&amp;rsquo;s platform to raise fund?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Answer&lt;/strong&gt;: Because our platform is a tool to replace traditional intermediaries. Moreover,our platform links with experts in art, designer ,financial, agribusiness as well as project initiators with committed supporters who believe strongly in the persons behind the projects to provide capital.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#008000&quot;&gt;Question:&lt;/span&gt; Who are the Creator and the Backer?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Answer&lt;/strong&gt;:The Creator is a person who creates the project and will receive a monetary payment. The Backer is person who donates or invest his/her money for the creator&amp;rsquo;s project.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#008000&quot;&gt;Question:&lt;/span&gt; Why do people support a project?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Answer&lt;/strong&gt;: Many people are rallying around their friends&amp;rsquo; creative projects; some are supporting a new effort from someone they&amp;rsquo;ve long admired. Some are just inspired by a new idea, while others are motivated to pledge by a project&amp;rsquo;s rewards &amp;mdash; a copy of what&amp;rsquo;s being produced, a limited edition, or a custom experience related to the project. Supporting a project is more than just pledging funds to a creator. It&amp;rsquo;s pledging your support to a creative idea that you want to see exist in the world&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#008000&quot;&gt;Question:&lt;/span&gt; How much does GotongRoyongFund charge for a successfully project?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Answer&lt;/strong&gt;: 5 (five) % fee is for successfully funded project.There is a different fee for Charity/non-profit organizations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#008000&quot;&gt;Question:&lt;/span&gt; How long is the maximum duration for raising fund?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Answer&lt;/strong&gt;: The maximum duration to raise fund is for two months (60 days).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#008000&quot;&gt;Question:&lt;/span&gt; Is there any limitation amount to create projects?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Answer&lt;/strong&gt;: No limitation amount on projects. You decide how much you are needed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#008000&quot;&gt;Question: &lt;/span&gt;What is funding all or nothing?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Answer&lt;/strong&gt;: All or Nothing is main part of our system. No one will be charged for a project unless it reaches its&amp;rsquo; funding goal. All funds will be returned to the Backers when the projects do not reach the target funded.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#008000&quot;&gt;Question:&lt;/span&gt; For unsuccessfully projects, is it possible to re-post a revise and improve version of the creator?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Answer&lt;/strong&gt;: Yes, it is very possible. The Creator allows re-posting its project as long as it has been revised.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#008000&quot;&gt;Question:&lt;/span&gt; What is not allowed as projects?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Answer&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;GotongRoyongFund cannot be used to raise money for causes, whether it&amp;rsquo;s the Red Cross or a scholarship, or for &amp;ldquo;fund my life&amp;rdquo; projects, like tuition or bills.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;Creators cannot offer equity or financial incentives (ownership, share of profits, repayment/loans, cash-value equivalents, etc).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;Projects cannot resell items or offer rewards not produced by the project or its creator.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;Creators cannot promise to donate a portion of funds raised or future revenue to a cause.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;Projects cannot offer rewards in bulk quantities (more than 10).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;GotongRoyongFund cannot be used to fund websites or apps focused on e-commerce, business, and social networking.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;GotongRoyongFund cannot be used to fund software projects not run by the developers themselves.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;GotongRoyongFund cannot be used to buy real estate.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;Projects cannot offer alcohol as a reward.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;Projects cannot offer genetically modified organisms as a reward.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;No self-help material (books, videos, etc). This includes projects that offer (or produce materials that offer) business, emotional, financial, health, medical, sex/seduction, or other self-help advice.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;No offensive material (hate speech, etc); pornographic material; or projects endorsing or opposing a political candidate.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;No tobacco, drugs, and drug paraphernalia; energy food and drinks; or nutritional supplements.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;No contests, raffles, coupons, gambling, or lifetime memberships.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;No bath, beauty, and cosmetic products; electronic surveillance equipment; eye wear (sunglasses, prescription glasses, and others); firearms, weapons, knives, weapon accessories, and replicas of weapons; medical, health, safety, and personal care products; or infomercial-type products.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', ''),
(3, 'Privacy Policy', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;The Site is operated by GotongRoyongFund,a subdivison of Koperasi Selaras (&amp;ldquo;GotongRoyongFund&amp;rdquo; or the &amp;ldquo;Company&amp;rdquo;). This page sets forth the &lt;strong&gt;Privacy Policy&lt;/strong&gt; (the &amp;ldquo;Policy&amp;rdquo;) for the website at www.GotongRoyongFund.co.id, all other sites owned and operated by GotongRoyongFund that redirect to www.GotongRoyongFund.co.id, and all sub domains (collectively, the &amp;ldquo;Site&amp;rdquo;), and the service owned and operated by the Company (together with the Site, the &amp;ldquo;Service&amp;rdquo;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;We take the responsibility of having your personal information very seriously. We use your personal information only for providing and improving the Service. We treat your personal information as we would and do treat our own.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;By using the Service, you consent to the collection and use of information in accordance with this Policy. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;The Company reserves the right, at its sole discretion, to modify or replace this Policy by posting the updated version on the Site. It is your responsibility to check this Policy periodically for changes. Your continued use of the Service following the posting of any changes to this Policy constitutes your acceptance of those changes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collection of Information&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;We may collect and process the following information about you:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;information (such as your name, email and postal address, telephone number, sex, and country of residence) that you provide by completing forms on the Site, including if you register as a user of the Service, subscribe to our newsletter, upload or submit any material through the Site, or request any information;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;your log-in and password details in connection with the account sign-in process;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;details of any requests or transactions made by you through the Service;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;communications you send to us, for example to report a problem or to submit queries, concerns, or comments regarding the Service or its content;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;information that you post to the Site in the form of comments or contributions to discussions; and&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;IP addresses.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Uses of Your Personal Information&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;We will use the personal information you provide to:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;identify you when you sign-in to your account;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;enable us to provide you with the Services;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;send you information we think you may find useful or which you have requested from us;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;present projects to you when you use the Service which we believe will be of interest based on your geographic location and previous use of the Service;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;administer your account with us;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;enable us to contact you regarding any question you make through the Service;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;analyze the use of the Service and the people visiting to improve our content and Services; and&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;use for other purposes that we may disclose to you when we request your information.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;Project Creators receive the email addresses of their backers if the project is successfully funded.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;We provide the verified personal or legal entity name to backers in their receipt emails. In the future we may provide these names to backers or other users on the project page or other areas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Email&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;We want to communicate with you only if you want to hear from us. We try to keep emails to a minimum and give you the ability to opt out when we can.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;We will send you email relating to your personal transactions. We will keep these emails to a minimum.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;You will also receive certain email notifications, for which you may opt-out.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;We may send you service-related announcements on rare occasions when it is necessary to do so.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px&quot;&gt;Third-Party Services&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;We never post anything to your accounts with Facebook, Twitter, or any other third-party sites without your permission.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Except for the purposes of providing the Services, we will not give your name or personal information to third parties.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Technology&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Cookies are small pieces of information which are issued to your computer when you visit a website and which store and sometimes track information about your use of the Service. GotongRoyongFund uses cookies to help recognize you as a repeat visitor, to improve the quality of our Service, and to try and make your browsing experience meaningful. When you enter our Site, our web server sends a cookie to your computer which allows us to recognize your computer but not specifically who is using it. By associating the identification numbers in the cookies with other customer information when, for example, you log-in to the Service, then we know that the cookie information relates to you. Some of the code and cookies used by our Service are served by us, and some are served by third parties who are delivering services on our behalf.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Disclosure&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Any personal information or content that you voluntarily disclose in public areas of the Site becomes publicly available and can be collected and used by other users. You should exercise caution before disclosing your personal information through these public venues.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;GotongRoyongFund&amp;rsquo;s Project Creators never receive users&amp;rsquo; credit card information.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Wrap-up&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;GotongRoyongFund reserves the right to disclose your personally identifiable information as required by law and when we believe that disclosure is necessary to protect our rights, or in the good-faith belief that it is necessary to comply with the law.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;To modify or delete the personal information you have provided to us, please log in and update your profile. We may retain certain information as required by law or for necessary business purposes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;On request, we will give you a copy of all the personal information about you that we hold. This information is subject to a fee not exceeding the prescribed fee permitted by law.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;People under 21 years old are not permitted to use GotongRoyongFund on their own, and so this privacy policy makes no provision for their use of the site.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Questions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;If you have questions or suggestions, please contact us.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', ''),
(4, 'Partner Terms', '&lt;div id=&quot;stcpDiv&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;These Partner Terms govern your use of GotongRoyongFund websites and services (the &amp;ldquo;&lt;strong&gt;Service&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;rdquo;) as a Partner. You also agree to be bound by the Terms &amp;amp; Conditions, our Privacy Policy, all applicable laws and all conditions or policies referenced here (collectively, the &amp;ldquo;&lt;strong&gt;Terms&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;rdquo;).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&amp;ldquo;Partner&amp;rdquo; is a corporation or other legal entity that includes approved Campaigns on its dedicated page (&amp;ldquo;&lt;strong&gt;Partner Page&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;rdquo;) using the Service. You, alone, approve individual Campaigns to be run on your Partner Page.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:rgb(0, 128, 0)&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Non-Profit&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;If you are a non-profit organizations, you are required to&amp;nbsp; present your licensed or registration papers to GotongRoyongFund .&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div id=&quot;stcpDiv&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:rgb(0, 128, 0)&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Provision for Partners Managing Payments&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;If you&amp;nbsp; are to manage Contributions on behalf of Campaign Owners who set up their Campaigns on your Partner Page, you are responsible for disbursing the Contributions to the Campaign Owner. You agree to indemnify, defend and hold GotongRoyongFund harmless from and against all claims, causes of action, liabilities and damages (including laws&amp;rsquo; fees and costs) resulting from and relating to your management and disbursement of Contributions in connection with your Campaign. Your promise survives termination of this letter or the Terms for any reason.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:rgb(0, 128, 0)&quot;&gt;Branded Partner Page Features&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;GotongRoyongFund provides the basic tools that you need to host, support and launch Campaigns from your Partner Page. These tools include:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Partner branded page hosted on GotongRoyongFund displaying all Partner-sourced Campaigns&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Partner branded display on all sourced Campaigns via Partner Ribbon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Access to Partner Reporting Dashboard&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Payment processing options for Partners handling Campaign payment and disbursements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Access to GotongRoyongFund educational materials including webinars, videos, print collateral and comprehensive online knowledge-base&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:rgb(0, 128, 0)&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Creating a Partner Page and Commitment to Marketing and Promotion of Campaigns&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Your Partner Page will be live as soon as you complete the Partner Page Setup Form (&amp;ldquo;&lt;strong&gt;Launch Date&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;rdquo;).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Accurate and complete information is required when creating your account and setting up and managing your Partner Page. You are responsible for making sure that the information on your Partner Page is up to date and accurate.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;You agree to demonstrate an ongoing commitment to increase your audience&amp;rsquo;s engagement with your Partner Page and Campaigns which may include any or all of the following activities:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;A press release or other public statement promoting your Partner Page and Campaigns to which both parties agree in writing (e-mail is sufficient).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Promoting your Partner Page on your website, blog, Facebook, Twitter or other social media outlets where available and using your best efforts to publicize our relationship in marketing and public relations materials.&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	&lt;ol&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;To the extent you receive and use the email addresses or other personally identifiable information of Users, you agree to comply with all legal and regulatory requirements in your use of such email addresses and information including, without limitation, CAN-SPAM and privacy laws and our Privacy Policy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Attending educational sessions provided by GotongRoyongFund and sharing those sessions and materials with your community.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:rgb(0, 128, 0)&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Changes to Terms&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;GotongRoyongFund may change these Partner Terms at any time, so please review the policies frequently. If&amp;nbsp; a material change is made, GotongRoyongFund may notify you in the Service, by email, by means of a notice on our home page, or other places we think appropriate. A &amp;ldquo;material change&amp;rdquo; will be determined at GotongRoyongFund sole discretion, in good faith, and using common sense and reasonable judgment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:rgb(0, 128, 0)&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Contact Us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;If you have any questions about these Partner Terms, the practices of this site, or your dealings with this Website or complaints, please contact us at helpdesk@gotongroyongfund.co.id or&amp;nbsp; call us at 6221-250-6616 or 6221-250-6359.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '');
INSERT INTO `tb_pages_content` (`id`, `code`, `content`, `content_in`) VALUES
(5, 'Terms & Conditions', '&lt;div id=&quot;stcpDiv&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Please read these Terms of Use (the &amp;ldquo;Agreement&amp;rdquo; or &amp;ldquo;Terms of Use&amp;rdquo;) carefully before using the services offered by Koperasi Selaras, or&amp;nbsp; a sub-divison of&amp;nbsp; Koperasi Selaras, GotongRoyongFund (together &amp;ldquo;GotongRoyongFund&amp;rdquo; or the &amp;ldquo;Company&amp;rdquo;). This Agreement sets forth the legally binding terms and conditions for your use of the website at www.GotongRoyongFund.co.id, all other sites owned and operated by GotongRoyongFund that redirect to www.GotongRoyongFund.co.id, and all sub domains (collectively, the &amp;ldquo;Site&amp;rdquo;), and the service owned and operated by the Company (together with the Site, the &amp;ldquo;Service&amp;rdquo;). By using the Service in any manner, including, but not limited to, visiting or browsing the Site or contributing content, information, or other materials or services to the Site, you agree to be bound by this Agreement.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Summary of Service&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;GotongRoyongFund is a platform where certain users (&amp;ldquo;Project Creators&amp;rdquo;) run campaigns to fund creative projects by offering rewards to raise money from other users (&amp;ldquo;Backers&amp;rdquo;). Through the Site, email, websites, and other media, the Service makes accessible various content, including, but not limited to, videos, photographs, images, artwork, graphics, audio clips, comments, data, text, software, scripts, projects, other material and information, and associated trademarks and copyrightable works (collectively, &amp;ldquo;Content&amp;rdquo;). Project Creators, Backers, and other visitors to and users of the Service (collectively, &amp;ldquo;Users&amp;rdquo;) may have the ability to contribute, add, create, upload, submit, distribute, facilitate the distribution of, collect, post, or otherwise make accessible (&amp;ldquo;Submit&amp;rdquo;) Content. &amp;ldquo;User Submissions&amp;rdquo; means any Content Submitted by Users.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Acceptance of Terms&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;The Service is offered subject to acceptance of all of the terms and conditions contained in these Terms of Use, including the Privacy Policy available at hhtps://www.GotongRoyongFund.co.id/privacy, and all other operating rules, policies, and procedures that may be published on the Site by the Company, which are incorporated by reference. These Terms of Use apply to every user of the Service. In addition, some services offered through the Service may be subject to additional terms and conditions adopted by the Company. Your use of those services is subject to those additional terms and conditions, which are incorporated into these Terms of Use by this reference.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;The Company reserves the right, at its sole discretion, to modify or replace these Terms of Use by posting the updated terms on the Site. It is your responsibility to check the Terms of Use periodically for changes. Your continued use of the Service following the posting of any changes to the Terms of Use constitutes acceptance of those changes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;The Company reserves the right to change, suspend, or discontinue the Service (including, but not limited to, the availability of any feature, database, or Content) at any time for any reason. The Company may also impose limits on certain features and services or restrict your access to parts or all of the Service without notice or liability.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;The Service is available only to individuals who are at least 21 years old (and at least the legal age in your jurisdiction). You represent and warrant that if you are an individual, you are at least 21 years old in Indonesia to form a binding contract, and that all registration information you submit is accurate and truthful. The Company reserves the right to ask for proof of age from you and your account may be suspended until satisfactory proof of age is provided. The Company may, in its sole discretion, refuse to offer the Service to any person or entity and change its eligibility criteria at any time. This provision is void where prohibited by law and the right to access the Service is revoked in those jurisdictions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Rules and Conduct&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;As a condition of use, you promise not to use the Service for any purpose that is prohibited by the Terms of Use or law. The Service is provided only for your own personal, non-commercial use (except as allowed by the terms set forth in the section of these Terms of Use titled, &amp;ldquo;Projects: Fundraising and Commerce&amp;rdquo;). You are responsible for all of your activity in connection with the Service. You shall not, and shall not permit any third party using your account to, take any action, or Submit Content, that:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;infringes any patent, trademark, trade secret, copyright, right of publicity, or other right of any other person or entity, or violates any law or contract;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;you know is false, misleading, or inaccurate;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;is unlawful, threatening, abusive, harassing, defamatory, libelous, deceptive, fraudulent, tortuous, obscene, offensive, profane, or invasive of another&amp;rsquo;s privacy;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;constitutes unsolicited or unauthorized advertising or promotional material or any junk mail, spam, or chain letters;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;contains software viruses or any other computer codes, files, or programs that are designed or intended to disrupt, damage, limit, or interfere with the proper function of any software, hardware, or telecommunications equipment or to damage or obtain unauthorized access to any system, data, password, or other information of the Company or any third party;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;is made in breach of any legal duty owed to a third party, such as a contractual duty or a duty of confidence; or&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;impersonates any person or entity, including any employee or representative of the Company.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Additionally, you shall not: (i) take any action that imposes or may impose (as determined by the Company in its sole discretion) an unreasonable or disproportionately large load on the Company&amp;rsquo;s or its third-party providers&amp;rsquo; infrastructure; (ii) interfere or attempt to interfere with the proper working of the Service or any activities conducted on the Service; (iii) bypass any measures the Company may use to prevent or restrict access to the Service (or other accounts, computer systems, or networks connected to the Service); (iv) run Mail list, Listserv, or any form of auto-responder or &amp;ldquo;spam&amp;rdquo; on the Service; or (v) use manual or automated software, devices, or other processes to &amp;ldquo;crawl&amp;rdquo; or &amp;ldquo;spider&amp;rdquo; any page of the Site.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;You shall not directly or indirectly: (i) decipher, decompile, disassemble, reverse engineer, or otherwise attempt to derive any source code or underlying ideas or algorithms of any part of the Service, except to the extent applicable laws specifically prohibit such restriction; (ii) modify, translate, or otherwise create derivative works of any part of the Service; or (iii) copy, rent, lease, distribute, or otherwise transfer any of the rights that you receive hereunder. You shall abide by all applicable local, state, national, and international laws and regulations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Project Creators agree to not abuse other users&amp;rsquo; personal information. Abuse is defined as using personal information for any purpose other than those explicitly specified in the Project Creator&amp;rsquo;s Project, or is not related to fulfilling delivery of a product or service explicitly specified in the Project Creator&amp;rsquo;s Project.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Registration&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;You may view Content on the Site without registering, but as a condition of using certain aspects of the Service, you may be required to register with the Company and select a screen name (&amp;ldquo;User ID&amp;rdquo;) and password. You shall provide accurate, complete, and updated registration information. Failure to do so shall constitute a breach of the Terms of Use, which may result in immediate termination of your account. You shall not use as a User ID, domain name, or project name any name or term that (i) is the name of another person, with the intent to impersonate that person; (ii) is subject to any rights of another person, without appropriate authorization; or (iii) is offensive, vulgar, or obscene. The Company reserves the right in its sole discretion to refuse registration of or cancel a User ID, domain name, and project name. You are solely responsible for activity that occurs on your account and shall be responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your password for the Site. You shall never use another User account without the other User&amp;rsquo;s express permission. You will immediately notify the Company in writing of any unauthorized use of your account, or other known account-related security breach.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Projects: Fundraising and Commerce&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;GotongRoyongFund is a platform where Project Creators run campaigns to fund creative projects by offering rewards to raise money from Backers. By creating a fundraising campaign on GotongRoyongFund, you as the Project Creator are offering the public the opportunity to enter into a contract with you. By backing a fundraising campaign on GotongRoyongFund, you as the Backer accept that offer and the contract between Backer and Project Creator is formed. GotongRoyongFund is not a party to that agreement between the Backer and Project Creator. All dealings are solely between Users.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;By backing or creating a fundraising campaign on GotongRoyongFund, you agree to be bound by this entire Agreement, including the following terms:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Backers agree to provide their payment information at the time they pledge to a campaign. The payment will be collected at or after the campaign deadline and only if the amount of money pledged as of the deadline is at least equal to the fundraising goal. The amount Backers pledge is the amount they will be charged.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Backers consent to GotongRoyongFund and its payments partners authorizing or reserving a charge on their payment or other payment method for any amount up to the full pledge at any time between the pledge and collection of the funds.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Backers agree to have sufficient funds available at the campaign deadline to ensure that the pledge will be collectible.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Backers may increase, decrease, or cancel their pledge at any time during the fundraising campaign, except that they may not cancel or reduce their pledge if the campaign is in its final 24 hours and the cancellation or reduction would drop the campaign below its goal.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;The Estimated Delivery Date listed on each reward is not a promise to fulfill by that date, but is merely an estimate of when the Project Creator hopes to fulfill by.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Project Creators agree to make a good faith attempt to fulfill each reward by its Estimated Delivery Date.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;For all campaigns, GotongRoyongFund gives to the Project Creator each Backer&amp;rsquo;s User ID and pledge amount. For successful campaigns, GotongRoyongFund additionally gives to the Project Creator each Backer&amp;rsquo;s name and email.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;For some rewards, the Project Creator needs further information from Backers, such as a mailing address or t-shirt size, to enable the Project Creator to deliver the rewards. The Project Creator shall request the information directly from Backers at some point after the fundraising campaign is successful. To receive the reward, Backers agree to provide the requested information to the Project Creator within a reasonable amount of time.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;GotongRoyongFund does not offer refunds. A Project Creator is not required to grant a Backer&amp;rsquo;s request for a refund unless the Project Creator is unable or unwilling to fulfill the reward.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Project Creators are required to fulfill all rewards of their successful fundraising campaigns or refund any Backer whose reward they do not or cannot fulfill.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Project Creators may cancel or refund a Backer&amp;rsquo;s pledge at any time and for any reason, and if they do so, are not required to fulfill the reward.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Because of occasional failures of payments from Backers, GotongRoyongFund cannot guarantee the receipt by Project Creators of the amount pledged minus fees.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;GotongRoyongFund and its payments partners will remove their fees before transmitting proceeds of a campaign. Fees may vary depending on region and other factors.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;GotongRoyongFund reserves the right to cancel a pledge at any time and for any reason.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;GotongRoyongFund reserves the right to reject, cancel, interrupt, remove, or suspend a campaign at any time and for any reason. GotongRoyongFund is not liable for any damages as a result of any of those actions. GotongRoyongFund&amp;rsquo;s policy is not to comment on the reasons for any of those actions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Project Creators should not take any action in reliance on having their project posted on the Site or having any of the money pledged until they have the ability to withdraw and spend the money. There may be a delay between the end of a successful fundraising campaign and access to the funds.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;GotongRoyongFund is not liable for any damages or loss incurred related to rewards or any other use of the Service. GotongRoyongFund is under no obligation to become involved in disputes between any Users, or between Users and any third party arising in connection with the use of the Service. This includes, but is not limited to, delivery of goods and services, and any other terms, conditions, warranties, or representations associated with campaigns on the Site. GotongRoyongFund does not oversee the performance or punctuality of projects. The Company does not endorse any User Submissions. You release GotongRoyongFund, its officers, employees, agents, and successors in rights from claims, damages, and demands of every kind, known or unknown, suspected or unsuspected, disclosed or undisclosed, arising out of or in any way related to such disputes and the Service.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Fees and Payments&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Joining GotongRoyongFund is free. However, we do charge fees for certain services. When you use a service that has a fee you have an opportunity to review and accept the fees that you will be charged. Changes to fees are effective after we provide you with notice by posting the changes on the Site. You are responsible for paying all fees and taxes associated with your use of the Service.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Funds pledged by Backers are collected by Koperasi Selaras. We accept only bank transfer from &lt;strong&gt;Bank Central Asia&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Bank Rakyat Indonesia&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;CimbNiaga.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Third-Party Sites&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif&quot;&gt;The Service may permit you to link to other websites or resources on the internet, and other websites or resources may contain links to the Site. When you access third-party websites, you do so at your own risk. Those other websites are not under the Company&amp;rsquo;s control, and you acknowledge that the Company is not liable for the content, functions, accuracy, legality, appropriateness, or any other aspect of those other websites or resources. The inclusion on another website of any link to the Site does